title: [Mischung's Outfitting]
[Mischung's Combat Gear]
description: A tattered merchant permit hangs on one of the smooth mistwood walls, and a glass-tiled vaulted ceiling rises overhead.  A worn rug sits in one corner of a sturdy planked floor.  There is a rusted metal display rack on one side of the shop and some stained driftwood shelves on the other.
